snippet.title: Sling Kings is Coming Soon (Song/Trailer)
snippet.description:
Chess is a centuries-old battleground of intellect. With an impossibly high ceiling for strategic planning, chess invites you to think hard about each move you make. Sometimes, however, you don't want to think hard; you want to think FAST.

That's why I made Sling Kings!
